headline.main: Bjork, Jamieson Still Tied for Lead at Tshwane Open
headline.print_headline: Bjork, Jamieson Still Tied for Lead at Tshwane Open

lead_paragraph: Alexander Bjork and Scott Jamieson will fight it out again as they retained a share of the lead heading toward the final round of the Tshwane Open on Saturday.
